title: Diamond 5 Jungle looking for ranked 5s team

embed.description: Check your Summoner statistics, MMR, realtime spectate and using powerful global LoL Charts!

body:
Hi all :)
I have been playing this game since season 1 and I main jungle, Udyr jungle...
Even though jungle is my main role I'm fairly well rounded at all roles and can play any position that I need to.
Looking for a team that's active and in need of a jungler preferably but can fill another position if desperately needed.

Cheers

replies.body: Hey I'm the coach of an upcoming team, we are currently looking for serious players who want to play with the best OCE has to offer

Hi, you are welcome to join us in any of out new 3 teams, we are a nice friendly social group growing up and learning, atm out teams are mainly formed by diamond players, free free to add me and join out adventure.
